<ul style="list-style-type:disc">

</ul>

<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">ProcessingInstruction
            </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">节点仅在</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> XML </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">文档中受支持，在</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> HTML </span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">文档中不支持。在这些中，处理指令将被视为注释并在树中表示为注释对象。</span></span></li>
</ul>

            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">声明不同。</span></span></li>
</ul>
